data.description: Nestled in an established neighborhood on a cul-de-sac in Von Elm East Sec II! Conveniently located close to the turnpike making it a breeze to comute anywhere around the okc metro area in no time! This Home features Tons of storage throughout! Living room area is generously sized with beautiful built-in shelving and crown molding, new ceiling fan, new ceiling and new flooring! Main bedroom is also generous in size and also has new floors, great walk-in closet, main on-suite bathroom has a brand new tiled shower. In the back, you'll find a large shed for extra storage and a nice sized covered patio perfect for enjoying sitting outside. Kitchen has a stainless steele dishwasher and a large utility room. Garage has been recently painted. Disclaimer:On this property the courthouse records on the land amount are incorrect at 1.5 acres. This is a normal sized city lot at approximately 0.16 acre. Sellers have just put in a brand new hot water heater tank.
